Package com.bluegosling.apt Description

APIs to simplify implementation of annotation processors and annotation processing tools.

This package contains an AbstractProcessor that feathers some more convenience functionality on top of the standard AbstractProcessor.

Also included are two sub-packages, one with a reflection API that wraps javax.lang.model.element and java.lang.model.type APIs and the other a JUnit4 test runner that allows for unit testing annotation processors from within an actual processing environment.
